article.description: — Austin Crowley had 22 points in Southern Miss' 77-52 victory against Winthrop on Tuesday.
article.headline: Southern Miss wins 77-52 over Winthrop
article.story: CANCUN, Mexico -- — Austin Crowley had 22 points in Southern Miss' 77-52 victory against Winthrop on Tuesday. Crowley added six steals for the Golden Eagles (5-0). Denijay Harris added 12 points while shooting 4 of 7 from the field and 4 for 6 from the line, and he also had seven rebounds. Felipe Haase shot 4 for 8, including 1 for 3 from beyond the arc to finish with nine points. Sin'Cere McMahon led the way for the Eagles (2-4) with 16 points. Kelton Talford added 14 points for Winthrop. Isaiah Wilson also had eight points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
